%% CLAUDE'S CHANGE INTERPRETATION
%% ========================================================
%% OBJECTIVE: Ensure failed implementations follow a structured rollback procedure before incident reporting, minimizing service disruption during change windows.
%%
%% EXPLANATION:
%% Inserted an "Execute Backout Plan" step between a failed implementation and the incident report. When implementation fails, the backout plan is executed first. A decision node checks whether the backout was successful — if not, the issue is escalated to Emergency CAB before proceeding to the incident report and change closure.
